snippet: Comments made on a television program led some to wonder whether important information in the Malaysia Airlines crash in Ukraine was being withheld.
abstract: Senior Dutch government official's disclosure that one victim of the Malaysia Airlines Flight 17 plane crash in eastern Ukraine had been found wearing an oxygen mask leads to dismay among investigators and outrage among victims' relatives.
lead_paragraph: Comments made on a television program led some to wonder whether important information in the Malaysia Airlines crash in Ukraine was being withheld.

headline.main: Dutch Official Criticized for Disclosure About Malaysian Plane Crash in Ukraine
headline.print_headline: Dutch Official’s Disclosure in Crash Inquiry Criticized
